# ---
Matlab scripts and subfunctions to load and plot the snapshot, media, metric, seismograms and coordinates generated from the CGFD3D-elastic packages.
Author:
    Yuanhang Huo (yhhuo@mail.ustc.edu.cn)
    Wei Zhang    (zhangwei@sustech.edu.cn)
Affiliation:
    University of Science and Technology of China
    Southern University of Science and Technology
Date:
    2021.06.09
# ---


+ --- Scripts to plot
+ draw_snap_pcolor.m
    Plot and save the seismic wavefield snapshot across a cross-section in pcolor style
+ draw_snap_surf.m
    Plot and save the seismic wavefield snapshot across a cross-section in surf style
+ draw_snap_surf_multi.m
    Plot and save the 3D seismic wavefield snapshot on multiple cross-sections in surf style
+ draw_slice_pcolor.m
    Plot and save the seismic wavefield snapshot on a slice in pcolor style
+ draw_slice_surf.m
    Plot and save the seismic wavefield snapshot on a slice in surf style
+ draw_slice_surf_multi.m
    Plot and save the seismic wavefield snapshot on multiple slices in surf style
+ draw_media_pcolor.m
    Plot and save the media across a cross-section in pcolor style
+ draw_media_surf.m
    Plot and save the media across a cross-section in surf style
+ draw_media_surf_multi.m
    Plot and save the 3D media on multiple cross-sections in surf style
+ draw_metric_pcolor.m
    Plot and save the metric data across a cross-section in pcolor style
+ draw_metric_surf.m
    Plot and save the metric data across a cross-section in surf style
+ draw_metric_surf_multi.m
    Plot and save the 3D metric data on multiple cross-sections in surf style
+ draw_seismo_line.m
    Plot and save the seismograms at the receivers and the whole line
+ draw_grid_coord.m
    Plot and save the grid/mesh generation and spacing


+ --- Necessary subfunctions to locate and gather data for the above drawing scripts
+ locate_snap.m
    Locate the processors/threads for the specific snapshot profile
+ locate_media.m
    Locate the processors/threads for the specific medium profile
+ locate_metric.m
    Locate the processors/threads for the specific metric profile
+ locate_coord.m
    Locate the processors/threads for the specific coordinates
+ gather_snap.m
    Gather and load the snapshot data
+ gather_media.m
    Gather and load the media data
+ gather_metric.m
    Gather and load the metric data
+ gather_coord.m
    Gather and load the coordinate data
 

